  "instructions": [
    "Combine coconut milk, fish sauce, lime juice, grated ginger, and garlic in a blender and puree until smooth.",
    "Heat the mixture in a saucepan over medium heat until warm.",
    "Stir in chopped pistachio and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in chopped Thai basil.",
    "Mix sodium alginate with water in a separate bowl.",
    "Drop the pistachio mixture by spoonfuls into the alginate bath.",
    "Let it sit for 2 minutes to allow spherification to occur.",
    "Remove the satay from the bath with a slotted spoon and serve immediately."
